        <briefdescription>
<para>This constructor registers the animatable property with the registered type. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This constructor is for scene-graph only properties where the value of the property can be retrieved and set via specified functions.</para>
<para>@SINCE_1_0.0 <parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">registered</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
